Package: linux-headers-powerpc
Architecture: powerpc
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: linux-headers-powerpc-smp
Description: Linux kernel headers on PowerPC
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for PowerPC.

