Architecture: powerpc
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: linux-image-powerpc-smp, linux-firmware
Description: Linux kernel image on PowerPC
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for PowerPC support.

Package: linux-powerpc
Architecture: powerpc
Section: restricted/metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: linux-powerpc-smp, linux-headers-powerpc
Description: Complete Linux kernel on PowerPC.
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel and headers
 for PowerPC.

